title: Mana v.1.7.4 - responsive multi-purpose Wordpress theme
description:
The Mana wordpress Theme is built upon Bootstrap 3.0 grid system and is fully responsive in design which will adapt to display in its correct proportions on all devices from small to large screens. Mana is also retina ready and looks amazing on modern super high pixel density devices.

Mana Theme is very flexible and simple to use thanks to the drag and drop page and post builder which lets you display content and page elements anywhere you want within your layout.

The advanced admin panel has over 135 different options to customize various design and functionality elements of your website. You also have the option to switch between a one page/scrolling layout and a traditional multi page design.

Mana Theme has you covered when it comes to sliders because you get 2 premium sliders included with the theme. The layer slider and the revolution slider are both extremely impressive and certainly add to the viewing experience of your websites visitors.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/mana-responsive-multipurpose-theme/5895568

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
